[[File:中華人民共和國國家安全法.jpg|thumbnail|National Security Law of People's Republic of China]]
'''National Security Law of People's Republic of China''' ({{zh|s=中华人民共和国国家安全法}}), which was issued on July 1, 2015, is a Chinese law made up by 7 sections containing 84 articles.the authority of the [[PRC]] says that this law can protect national security of the PRC effectively and the medias controlled by the authority praise the law, while some analysts think that the authority can restrict Chinese people's freedom by this law.<ref name=Xinhua1>{{cite web|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/politics/2015-07/01/c_1115787097.htm|title=聚焦新国家安全法五大亮点|publisher=新华网|language=Chinese|accessdate=2015-07-03}}</ref><ref name=NOS>{{cite web|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2015-07-02/155932060692.shtml|title=国家安全法昨通过施行|publisher=新安晚报|language=Chinese|accessdate=2015-07-03}}</ref>

[[Annette Lu]], the formal Vice President of [[Taiwan]], said that this law is an offense to Taiwan, and some people from [[Hong Kong]] concern about their safety while stay in the [[Mainland China]] after this law was issued.<ref name=BBC2>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2015/07/150703_taiwan_former-vp_annette_lu_hsiu-lien_panama-city|title=呂秀蓮：中國國安法顯示併吞台灣急迫感|publisher=BBC}}</ref><ref name=BBC1>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2015/07/150703_china_national_security_law_reax|title=外界對中國國安法如何付諸實施表達關注|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2015-07-03}}</ref>

